verbose_text: Endothelial MHC class II expression was detected in donor heart 7 mum cryostat sections by double labeling with rat anti-mouse CD31 (clone MEC 13.3; BD Pharmingen) detected with Cy3 conjugated goat anti-rat IgG and FITC conjugated rat anti-mouse I-E (clone 14-4-45; BD Pharmingen) followed by FITC conjugated rat anti-mouse I-A b (clone AF6-120.11; BD PharMingen).
